How to Import Fan Token in Metamask

Connect to Metamask and click the appropriate "Add to Metamask" button and follow the instructions in metamask, or follow the steps below.
  • Click the Metamask add-on icon.
  • Click "Import tokens" at the bottom of the assets list.
  • Switch to "Custom Token" tab.
  • Fill the form with one of these parameters (Note: Only address is required, the rest should be populated automatically):
{{$counter := 0}} {{range $symbol, $bep2eInfo := .Bep2eInfos}} {{if lessThanHalf $counter}}
  • Symbol: {{$symbol}}
  • Address: {{$bep2eInfo.Contract}}
{{end}} {{$counter = (inc $counter)}} {{end}}
{{$counter = 0}} {{range $symbol, $bep2eInfo := .Bep2eInfos}} {{if moreThanHalf $counter}}
  • Symbol: {{$symbol}}
  • Address: {{$bep2eInfo.Contract}}
{{end}} {{$counter = (inc $counter)}} {{end}}
  • Click "Add Custom Token" to proceed.
  • Click "Import Tokens" and the token type will be added to your wallet.
